      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/95142c2955e1896817dc3d6ff9639ac5_4782676490087251437.png",
                "id": "talent44763",
                "key": "Akara",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Akara"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, applies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seed of Skandha</span> to target character. If the target character already had <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seed of Skandha</span> applied to them, then apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seed of Skandha</span> to all opposing characters instead.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Seed of Skandha</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">After any character who has a Seed of Skandha takes Elemental Reaction DMG</span>: Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Piercing DMG</span> to the character(s) to which the Seed of Skandha is attached on the same side of the field.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/9ee7deb6582de98819a51f65d4d0a5e4_596695137747920189.png",
                "id": "talent41448",
                "key": "All Schemes to Know",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "All Schemes to Know"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. Applies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seed of Skandha</span> to all opposing characters.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Seed of Skandha</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After any character who has a Seed of Skandha takes Elemental Reaction DMG</span>: Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to the character(s) to which the Seed of Skandha is attached on the same side of the field.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/a50ede7c08761d3a5bd17f505692ff2b_2661516358861666581.png",
                "id": "talent26511",
                "key": "All Schemes to Know: Tathata",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "All Schemes to Know: Tathata"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shrine of Maya</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shrine of Maya</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When your character triggers an Elemental Reaction</span>: +1 additional DMG.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/f1d75a58813affc77a8ed61da0fac236_6108933993033551738.png",
                "id": "talent53832",
                "key": "Illusory Heart",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Illusory Heart"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_4565845487108374373.png",
                "id": "talent56019",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds) </span>runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3554565676843159109.png",
                "id": "talent90389",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
